text: Oreste Muzzi (7 July 1887 - 1946) was an Italian swimmer. He competed in the men's 1500 metre freestyle event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1887 births Category:1946 deaths Category:Italian male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Italy Category:Swimmers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Florence Category:Italian male freestyle swimmers
